Author: Birdie49
Text: You're not faking it. I'm in almost the exact same situation -- been browsing ED sites since I was a kid but didn't restrict until later, currently eating pretty much at my TDEE, all that stuff.  Listen. If you still have that voice in your head, if you've ever had that voice in your head, there's a good chance you're disordered in some way. Healthy people don't think like we do, and even though it seems normal after awhile, normal for us isn't necessarily healthy. You are not faking it. You are 100% valid and 100% worthy of love and support and recovery. I promise. And I am so, so proud of you for even taking steps towards getting better.
